ed="T" n="0872c21"/><persName key="A013635">釋法成</persName>，本姓<name>王</name>，名<persName key="A013635">守慎</persName>，官至監察御史<ptr target="#n2038"/>。屬<lb
ed="T" n="0872c22"/><persName key="A002099">天后</persName>猜貳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2061"/>，信酷吏羅織<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2062"/>，乃避法官，乞出家為<lb
ed="T" n="0872c23"/>僧<ptr target="#n2098"/>。苦節勤於化導，聲發響隨，行高質直。<date key="j19774281978588" notAfter-iso="+0705-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0701-11-30"><name>長<lb
ed="T" n="0872c24"/>安</name>中</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000057509"><placeName>京兆</placeName><placeName>西市</placeName></placeName>疏鑿大坎，號曰「海池」<lb
ed="T" n="0872c25"/>焉──支分<placeName key="PL000000055427">永安渠</placeName>以注之，以為放生之所。池<lb
ed="T" n="0872c26"/>上佛屋經樓，皆<persName key="A013635">成</persName>所造。穿池之際，獲古石，<lb
ed="T" n="0872c27"/>銘云「百年為市，而後為池。」自<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋朝</placeName>置都立<lb
ed="T" n="0872c28"/>市，至于時正一百年矣<ptr target="#n2988"/>。<date key="j19683711968724" notAfter-iso="+0678-01-30" notBefore-iso="+0677-02-11"><name>儀鳳</name>二年</date>，望氣者<lb
ed="T" n="0872c29"/>云：「此坊<ptr target="#n2039"/>有異氣。」勅掘之，得石函，函內貯佛<pb ed="T" n="0873a" xml:id="T50.2061.0873a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0873a01"/>舍利萬餘粒，光色粲爛而堅剛。勅於此處<lb
ed="T" n="0873a02"/>造<placeName key="PL000000042151">光宅寺</placeName>，仍散舍利於<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>寺及諸州府各<lb
ed="T" n="0873a03"/>四十九粒。<persName key="A002099">武后</persName>於此始置<placeName key="PL000000055415">七寶臺</placeName>，遂改寺<lb
ed="T" n="0873a04"/>額，<persName key="A013635">成<roleName>公</roleName></persName>居之。行其激勸，多以崇福<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2063"/>為<anchor xml:id="beg0873sgsz1"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0873sgsz1"/>任<lb
ed="T" n="0873a05"/>焉。</p>
